Package gui

Class CalculatedTransportationEventBox

java.lang.Object
gui.CalculatedTransportationEventBox
All Implemented Interfaces:
EventBox, Serializable
public class CalculatedTransportationEventBox extends Object implements EventBox, Serializable
A class that represents the transportation event whose arrival time is calculated based on the distance to the destination and speed of travel. Implements the EventBox and Serializable interfaces
